DarkMouse::
She looked as Bezerk got ready to attack Apocoplyse. "Beserk. Don't 
do it.  Besides, I need you in good shape. You need to be in one 
peice if your going to slaughter our enemies." she said with a slight 
grin on her face. The thought of killing an allience member just put 
a grin on her face.
